Title: ChecksumGUI
Description:
ChecksumGUI is a simple Windows application to compute file or text hash.

It supports MD5, SHA1, SHA256, SHA384 and SHA512 algorithms.

ChecksumGUI is based on .Net Framework 4 and WPF.
